data.chText: 海军将官；海军上将；舰队司令
data.enText: an officer of very high rank in the navy

data.chText: 舰队司令视察了他所统率的军舰。
data.enText: The admiral visited the ships under his command.

tr: any of several brightly colored butterflies
the supreme commander of a fleet
ranks above a vice admiral and below a fleet admiral

value.def: An admiral is a very senior officer who commands a navy.
